Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.99,0:00:06.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）山陽(さんよう)を巡る戦は\N秦国(しんこく)軍の勝利で終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:06.35,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,The war over Shanyang ended with the State of Qin Army's victory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:11.16,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,and Lian Po returned to the capital of Daliang as the general of a losing army.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:11.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗(れんぱ)は敗軍の将として\N王都 大梁(だいりょう)に戻っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:15.17,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,L-Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:15.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（景湣王(けいびんおう)）れ… 廉頗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:20.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）許されざる大失態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.09,0:00:20.65,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,This was an unforgivable disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:24.52,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,If you so decree it, King of Wei, then I will not object to being decapitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏王(ぎおう)の命とあらば\N斬首でも文句はない！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.06,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（景湣王）何を言う！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:29.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そちが魏国(ぎこく)のために\N最良の選択をしてくれたことは―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:31.62,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,I'm gravely aware that you made choices that were the best for the State of Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:31.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,重々 分かっておる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:35.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは そちを責める気など\Nみじんもないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.89,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,I haven't the least intention of condemning you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:43.40,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,However, evading execution is the limit of my power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:43.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃが 死刑を回避することが\Nわしの限界じゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許せ 廉頗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.89,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:51.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そなたを魏国から追放する
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:52.42,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,I must banish you from the State of Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:53.91,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,According to historical records,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:55.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）「史書」によれば\N廉頗は魏国ののち
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:59.76,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,that after leaving the State of Wei, Lian Po fled to the State of Chu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:59.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,更に 楚(そ)の国へと亡命したとある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:04.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙国(ちょうこく)の英雄 廉頗は\N結局 祖国に戻ることなく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:01.67,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,The hero of the State of Zhao, Lian Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:07.00,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,would never return to his homeland in his lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:07.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生涯の幕を下ろすのである
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:13.93,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs80\be0.2\c&H000000&\pos(634,106)}The Strategist Arrives
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:20.28,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Xiang!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（陽(よう)）向(こう)ちゃん！\N（向）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:23.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（陽）\Nおはよう　朝から ご機嫌だね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:21.98,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.27,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,You sure seem to be in a good mood this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:26.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（向）\Nえっ？ あっ 実は ゆうべ 伽(とぎ)で…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.95,Kingdom-Main,Xiang,0,0,0,,The truth is that last night... As an attendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.66,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Wh-What, what, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか… まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:34.39,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（向）\Nああっ！ ちち… 違う！ 違うよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:36.16,Kingdom-Main,Xiang,0,0,0,,N-N-No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:37.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆうべは何もなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:37.58,Kingdom-Main,Xiang,0,0,0,,Nothing happened last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:42.70,Kingdom-Main,Xiang,0,0,0,,I-It's just that since the war ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:39.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,た… ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:44.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦が終わって 大王さまが\Nとても うれしそうだったから…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.50,Kingdom-Main,Xiang,0,0,0,,his highness seemed very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:46.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（陽）え～っ？ なに？ それ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:47.04,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Huh? What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:51.55,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Geez, you two really haven't progressed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:51.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…ていうか 向ちゃんたちって\N本当に進展ないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この前の事件で\N少しはアレかと思ったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:55.62,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,With that incident before, I thought it might be {\i1}that{\i0} but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:59.97,Kingdom-Main,Xiang,0,0,0,,Um, well it wasn't completely devoid of any of that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:59.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,い… いや その…\N全くないわけではないけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ 何か言った？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:01.63,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:04.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… ううん 何でもない！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.14,Kingdom-Main,Xiang,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信(しん)）ンンッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:15.82,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,What are those clothes you're wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君(しょうぶんくん)）何じゃ？ その格好は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:18.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで\N論功行賞の式典に出るつもりか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:19.10,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Do you intend to enter the distribution of honors ceremony like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）えっ？ ダ… ダメなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:21.71,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Huh?! What, no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:24.32,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But this is all I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:24.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つうか 俺 これしか持ってねえし…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:31.08,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose wearing armor is allowed, so perhaps that would be acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:28.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）\Nま… まあ 甲冑(かっちゅう)が許されているので
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:31.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメということはなかろうが…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:33.53,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That's all? I was panicking there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだよ 焦ったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:37.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get going to that distribution of honors ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:37.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んじゃ 早く行こうぜ\N論功行賞ってやつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:40.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハッ！\Nなに？ 俺 褒められんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.55,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What? Not gonna praise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ…\Nまったく お前というヤツは…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.84,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Honestly, you never change...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:46.23,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Distribution of honors ceremony, what'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:46.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）論功行賞！ どうしよう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）なに見てんだよ おっさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:53.10,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,What're you lookin' at, old man?! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この短い間に よくも ここまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:03:00.52,Kingdom-Thought,Chang,0,0,0,,He's done well to make it this far in such a short time. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.86,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What're you lookin' at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:04.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに見てやがる…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:09.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）\N本当に大したヤツじゃ 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.80,Kingdom-Thought,Chang,0,0,0,,You're really quite a man, Xin! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何すんだ おっさん てめえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.75,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What're you doing, you old bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:18.61,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Today's ceremony will be a big one. All of the prominent people of the imperial court will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:18.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は 朝廷の有力者が\N勢ぞろいする大きな式典だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.60,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,So try your hardest not to be careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,粗相のないように\Nくれぐれも気をつけろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:24.18,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I know, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\N分かってるよ！ うっせえなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:32.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）す… すっげえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.77,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,A-Awesome! {Thoughrt}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:36.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,や… やべえ…\Nなんか意外と緊張するな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:36.99,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,A-Aw man, I'm actually kinda nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ者(もん) お前は後ろじゃ！ 下がれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:37.93,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:40.07,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,You're in the back! Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ 何だ？ おっさん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.90,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Huh? What, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬(もうてん)）\Nこっちだよ！ 恥ずかしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.51,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,This way. How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 蒙恬！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:46.96,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Meng Tian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王賁(おうほん)も来てんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.66,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Is Wang Ben here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:54.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 玉鳳(ぎょくほう)隊は\Nまだ山陽の守備に当たってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.91,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,No, the Yufeng Unit is still stationed to defend Shanyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:58.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！ つうか お前 変な格好だな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:58.86,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Say, you've got some weird clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.04,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:01.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が言うな…\N（土門(どもん)）お前ら うるさいぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.67,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Would you two pipe down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:06.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（秦国大臣）皆の者 拝礼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:06.68,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Everyone, pay your respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:11.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大王さまのご入殿である
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:11.56,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,His highness is entering the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:23.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）あれが大王か…\Nここからじゃ よく見えないな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.12,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,So that's the king? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:23.35,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,I can't really see him too well from here. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）オッ… いつもと服が違う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.66,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Oh, his outfit's different from normal. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:30.56,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,And now, the distribution of honors ceremony will commence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:30.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（呂不韋(りょふい)）それでは\Nこれより論功行賞を始める
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.79,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Lü Buwei!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呂不韋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:37.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういや ここにいる連中の半分は\N政(せい)の敵なんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:37.48,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, half the people here are Zheng's enemies. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:42.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回は まず\N特に功の厚かった３人を賞する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:43.08,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,Today, we will be starting with the three men whom rendered the largest achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:48.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この３人には 特別に大王さまより\Nじきじきに祝いの剣が授与される
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:48.38,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,These three will be receiving a congratulatory sword from the king himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:51.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では 昌平君(しょうへいくん)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:51.47,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,Now then, Changpingjun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:52.81,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは 第１功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:05:01.90,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,To begin, the first achievement, the Supreme Commander that led the State of Qin Army to victory, General Meng Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:05:01.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国軍を勝利に導いた総大将\N蒙驁(もうごう)将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）フォ…\N（武人たち）オオッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:09.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オオッ… 蒙驁将軍！\Nすっげえ歓声だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.79,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,General Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.86,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What a cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The general's court rank will increase by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌平君）将軍には爵位を１つ昇級
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.72,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,he will be given land in Jiabai and Shan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:18.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佳白(かはく)と禅(ぜん)の地を与え\N金2,000と宝物10点を与える
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:18.72,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,given 2,000 gold and 10 treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）\N大儀であった　体をいたわるように
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.00,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Thank you for your sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.73,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Please take care of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）フォハ… ありがたく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.33,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続いて 第２功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.99,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,Continuing on, the second achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:37.15,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,The Vice General that slew an enemy staff officer and the enemy Supreme Commander, General Huan Ji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:35.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵参謀と総大将を討ち取った副将…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桓騎(かんき)将軍\N（歓声）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.04,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Good on ya, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（中貴(ちゅうき)）よっ！ お頭\N（雷土(らいど)）待ってました！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.23,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:45.34,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,The general will rise two court ranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:45.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌平君）将軍には爵位２階級昇級
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:48.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,青卑(せいひ) 青林(せいりん) 更に大苛(だいか)の地を与え
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:48.86,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,receive land in Qingbei, Ginglin, as well as Daike,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金2,000と宝物10点を与える
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.53,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,and given 2,000 gold and 10 treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.68,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Thank you for your sacrifices, General Huan Ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大儀であった 桓騎将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:55.74,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（桓騎）ありがたく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:01.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この者が\N秦国の隠れた逸材といわれる桓騎か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:01.11,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,So this is the man said to be one of the State of Qin's great hidden talents, Huan Ji? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:06.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつが 丞相(じょうしょう)に権力\N取られてるっつう ウチの王さまか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:06.36,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,So this is our king, the guy whose power is being taken by the chancellor? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなツラしてやがる…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.55,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,What sorta face has he got? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やりやしたね お頭！\N（笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.85,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,You really did it, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:33.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？ あの目は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.90,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,What're with those eyes? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.45,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,He's a puppet with a sheltered upbringing... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,温室育ちの木偶(でく)のくせに…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:40.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで あんなに猛(たけ)った光を\N帯びていやがる…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:40.20,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,Why were those eyes tinged with such a fierce light? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.54,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,Continuing, the third achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続いて 第３功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の主力たる将軍を\N自ら討ち取った―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:47.25,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,A man that slew the enemy general which was the enemy's primary force,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:51.50,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,the 300-Man General, Xin of the Feixin Unit! Come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:50.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,三百人将 飛信(ひしん)隊 信\N（信）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌平君）前へ\N（信）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:56.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（文官Ａ）なんだって？\N（文官Ｂ）三百人将で第３の功を？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:53.75,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:56.26,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A 300-Man General received the third highest achievement?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:07:02.71,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,For this war, he had temporarily been promoted to the rank of Thousand-Man General.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回の戦においては―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:03.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臨時的に千人将に昇格し\N戦ったとある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,三百人将 飛信隊 信\N前へ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:07.19,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,300-Man General, Xin of the Feixin Unit, forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ざわめき）\N（信）お… お… はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.98,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ah, uh, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:14.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（文官Ｃ）うん？ あれが…\N（文官Ｄ）臨時昇格で第３の功を？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:11.97,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.74,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Someone who was temporarily promoted received the third achievement?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:18.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だ… 大丈夫か？ お前\N（信）うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.52,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土門）ウワッ… お… おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.54,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.50,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ～あ… ダメだ こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.50,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Ah, this isn't going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:27.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… 何やってんだ 俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.32,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,What am I doing? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.50,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,My body won't do what I tell it to... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,か… 体が言うこと聞かねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（武官１）\Nワハハッ！ 何だ あの歩き方は！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.31,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What's with that walk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.16,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,His face looks so stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:37.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（武官２）顔が固まっておる！\N（信）クッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:49.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,場をにぎやかすのは\Nそのくらいで十分だぞ 信どの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:49.02,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,I think you've stirred up more than enough excitement here, Lord Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笑い声）\N（信）うるせえ！ わざとだ わざと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.15,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Sheddep! That was all on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オッ… 緊張が取れた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.24,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,He's not nervous anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:03.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌平君）それでは 第３功\N飛信隊の信には 爵位を３階級昇級
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:01.20,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,Now then, the third achievement, Xin of the Feixin Unit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:06.39,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,will increase three court ranks and receive 500 gold and 5 treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金500に宝物５点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:12.21,Kingdom-Main,Chan,0,0,0,,And he will now officially rise to the rank of Thousand-Man General!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 正式に―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,千人将へ昇格するものとする\N（信）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:16.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正式に… 千人将に！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:16.47,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Officially become a Thousand-Man General?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.86,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,All riiiiight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:22.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）こ… こら！\N（笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.65,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:26.33,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Xin of the Feixin Unit, thank you for your sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:25.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊 信 大儀であった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:28.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ウッ…\Nど… どうすりゃいいんだ？ 政
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.22,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Uh, what do I do, Zheng?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アア…\N前の２人を見てなかったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.79,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Weren't you looking at the other two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.49,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Get on one knee and say "thank you"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,片膝ついて“ありがたく”だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがたく
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.10,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）なぜかは分からないが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:51.92,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,Though it was not clear why, at this moment, all those watching were mesmerized by the sight of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:51.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このとき ２人の姿は\N見ている者たちの心を奪った
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.63,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,Despite the great difference between the king and the unit captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:54.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王と部隊長という落差がありながら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:59.09,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,for some reason the sight of them together seemed all too "fitting".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:59.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜか この２人の姿は\Nあまりにも しっくり来ていた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:04.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう美しさに\N皆が一瞬 静まり返り　そして…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:04.44,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,Seeing such beauty, everyone went silent in an instant and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:14.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の瞬間には\N大きな歓声へと変わった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:13.96,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,in the next instant, that changed to great cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.64,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,But for those two in the center of it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:17.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが その中心にいた２人は―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ\N込み上げる笑いをこらえるのに―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:22.57,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,it was all they could to do quell the laughter welling up inside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:23.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,精いっぱいだったという
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:28.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（呂不韋）ひとまず終わったな\N（李斯(りし)）はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.43,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,It's done for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.12,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:32.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では そろそろ わしの戦も再開じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:32.63,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,So my war will be restarting again, soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:38.13,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,I wonder who will be present at the next distribution of honors ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:38.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の論功行賞の場にいるのは\N果たして 誰かのぅ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）しかたないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:43.70,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,It's nothing to be concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふだんのお前を知る者なら\N笑わずにいられるか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:46.66,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,One can't help but laugh with it being someone you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:50.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）うるせえ！ こっちだって\N今更 お前と あんなこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:50.07,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Sheddep! Doing something like that with you after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Oh, right. There's something I had to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ そうだ！ これ\N言っとかなきゃいけねえんだった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:04.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は ただ 大将軍になるだけじゃ\N足らなくなっちまったぜ 政
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:04.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Just becoming a Great General isn't gonna be enough for me, Zheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:09.38,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It looks like your path is overlapping with mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:09.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやら 俺とお前の道が\Nひとつに重なったみてえなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）道が？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.41,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Your path?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:15.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中華統一だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Uniting China!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:28.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）\Nわしらでも なしえなかった大業を\Nやってのければ―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:28.43,Kingdom-Flashback,Lian,0,0,0,,If you achieve something great that even we could not achieve, {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:31.96,Kingdom-Flashback,Lian,0,0,0,,history will surely revere you! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歴史は 必ず貴様らをあがめる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:34.98,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Something great no one's ever done before? {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なしえなかった大業…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.39,Kingdom-Flashback,Lian,0,0,0,,Yeah. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:41.23,Kingdom-Flashback,Lian,0,0,0,,The uniting of China. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:41.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中華の統一じゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:46.42,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,I see. Lian Po said that, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:46.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）\Nそうか… 廉頗が そう言ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah. He said to blow away the old legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:49.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nああ 伝説の塗り替えってやつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:55.46,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,For that, you need a king's power and an army's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:55.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのためには 軍の力と王さまの力\N両方が必要だってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:57.73,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 正直なとこ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:01.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺には 国がどうとかは\Nよく分かんねえんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:01.27,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I don't know much about kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:05.47,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Of course, it hit home for me, knowing how huge it is to do that sorta thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが\Nとてつもねえ大事(おおごと)だってのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがにピンと来る
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:09.97,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,That is because it is a great deed that no one has ever been able to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:10.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いまだ 誰１人\Nなしえたことがない偉業だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:14.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偉業か！ ヘヘッ… いい響きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:12.66,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,A great deed, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:13.98,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:17.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その道に立つまでにも\N障害が多いがな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:17.82,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Though there will be many obstacles on that road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.49,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Then we've gotta go at it with full force!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから\N力みなぎるっつう話だろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:29.91,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Zheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:30.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やってやろうぜ 政！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:31.71,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.88,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs60\be0.2\pos(918,685)}Ying Zheng
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:49.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）論功行賞から数か月後\N山陽地方の里井(りせい)では―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.21,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Several months after the distribution of honors ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:50.61,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,in Lijing, a place nearby Shanyang,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:54.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いまだ 秦国軍と魏国軍による\N小競り合いが続いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:54.47,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,small skirmishes between the State of Qin Army and the State of Wei Army still continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.31,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Emergency report!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令Ａ）急報！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:01.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令Ａ）\N第１隊 第２隊 壊滅しました！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:00.93,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The first and second units have been wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:04.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備隊長）\Nクッ… ええい 援軍は まだか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.07,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Are the reinforcements ready yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:06.20,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Th-They're here! It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令Ｂ）\Nき… 来ました 彼らです！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼ら？\N（伝令Ｂ）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:07.45,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:13.46,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, the independent Thousand-Man Unit that played an active role in that war at Shenyang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:13.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの山陽の戦いで\N大活躍をした独立遊軍の千人部隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊です！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:22.19,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:22.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）…っし！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:25.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくぞ てめえら！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:25.84,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Let's go, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.10,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Meng Tian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（陸仙(りくせん)）蒙恬さま
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:43.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）おお 戻ったか！\Nお疲れさん　戦果は？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:40.86,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Ah, back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.31,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Thanks for all the hard work. How'd the battle turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.37,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（陸仙）いつもどおり\N適当に山へ押し返しましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.69,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We pushed them back into the mountains a fair amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）さすが一番隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.49,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,That's our best captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.20,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,By the way, Lu Xian,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:51.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ところでさ 陸仙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:55.43,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,these Wei women sure have something gorgeous about them, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:55.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏国の女性って\Nやっぱり どこか華やかだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:58.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どの人も みんな美人に見える
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:58.00,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,They all look so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:01.50,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Anyhow, I heard a rather odd rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:01.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（陸仙）それよりも\Nひとつ妙なウワサを耳にしました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,At the base at the front lines of Lijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里井の前線基地ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.53,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Ah, that's where the Feixin Unit is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ そこ 飛信隊がいるらしいね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:11.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正式に千人隊になって\N張り切ってるだろうなぁ あいつら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:11.93,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,They must be working hard now that they're officially a Thousand-Man Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵さん かわいそう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.72,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I feel bad for their enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:18.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ それが その飛信隊なのですが\N（蒙恬）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:17.12,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, about that Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Due to their consecutive defeats,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:20.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（陸仙）なんでも連戦連敗で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:24.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,their captain, Xin, is in danger of losing his title of Thousand-Man General, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隊長の信は\N千人将剥奪の危機らしいんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.66,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また負けた…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また負けたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.24,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ！\N（蹴る音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:45.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,い… 一体\Nどうなってんだ？ こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.55,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:50.33,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ever since the new Feixin Unit was formed... we haven't had a single victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:50.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新生飛信隊になって ここまで\Nたったの１勝もしてねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:54.56,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Do you guys just stop trying if it's not a big war, dammit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえら\Nでっけえ戦じゃねえからって―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:54.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手ぇ抜いてんじゃねえのか こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竜有(りゅうゆう)）\Nそ… そんなわけねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:57.07,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,N-No, we don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.56,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Hey, Xin, don't pin this on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平(びへい)）おい 信 俺らに当たるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえ 尾平！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.32,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Shut up, Wei Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:05.73,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It's been like this ever since you guys got new armor and started taking an interest in women!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:05.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大体 お前ら 甲冑とか新しくして\N色気づいてるから こんなことに…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕(えん)）信どの 落ち着いて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.07,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥(きょがい)）しっかし マジな話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:12.78,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,But seriously, why can we suddenly not win anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで\N俺たち 急に勝てなくなったんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（澤圭(たくけい)）敵も千人将ぐらいで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:18.86,Kingdom-Main,Zu,0,0,0,,The enemy Thousand-Man Generals aren't even well-known military commanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:18.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名だたる武将が\Nいるわけでもないんですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:23.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昂(こう)）やっぱり 羌瘣(きょうかい)副長が\N抜けたのが大きいんじゃないかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:23.04,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,I guess Vice Captain Qiang Lei not being here really has made a big difference, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）あっ…\N（信）ざけんな 昂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Quit screwing around, Ang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:30.34,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei hasn't rendered all of the achievements we got up to this point alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:29.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これまで 羌瘣が１人で\N武功を上げてたわけじゃねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:34.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつ１人抜けたからって\Nそこまで弱くなるかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:34.36,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,There's no way we'd get this much weaker because of one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.10,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,Um, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昂）いや そうじゃなくて\Nおいらが言ってんのは戦術の話だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.35,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,What I'm talking about is battle strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ 戦術？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:41.35,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,Battle strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:46.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって これまでって 羌瘣副長が\N作戦 全部 考えてたんでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:46.86,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,I mean, Vice Captain Qiang Lei has been thinking all of them up so far, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.01,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,N-Now that you mention it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田有(でんゆう)）そ… そういえば そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも その代わりに\N今は楚水(そすい)副長が作戦を…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:55.62,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,But Vice Captain Chu Shui has been doing it in her place now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楚水じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:15:01.37,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,No, he hasn't. Chu Shui's been busy with preparing supplies and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:01.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楚水は補給の手配とか\Nそっちで忙しいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:05.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\Nじゃ 今 作戦は誰が考えて…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:05.63,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Then who's been coming up with the strategies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.38,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Mr. Yuan and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と渕さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:14.76,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）それだー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:17.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえ 何してくれてんだ こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:17.26,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What've you been doing, dammit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:20.27,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Do you know how much damage we've suffered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これまで どんだけ被害が出たと\N思ってんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待て てめえら！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.12,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:25.02,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Who decided it was the strategies that've been the cause of all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに 勝手に\N作戦が原因って決めつけてんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.69,Kingdom-Main,Qi,0,0,0,,There's nothing else it could be, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以外ねえだろう このボケが！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかげんにしろよ 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Cut the crap, Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:33.04,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You're one of the dumbest ones here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえの頭の悪さは\N下から何番目かだろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:35.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信 あんまりだよ！\N（信）クッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.27,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,Xin, this is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）\Nやっぱり そんなことだったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:39.73,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I thought that might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）あっ 蒙恬！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.93,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Meng Tian!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おひさ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:45.31,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Good ta see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:47.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）だからよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.18,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.80,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,these guys zoom out like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちがダーッと行って\Nドカ～ンとやって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:54.80,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,these guys go ka-boom and after that if the mounted unit ka-bam then we'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:54.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは騎馬隊でガガッとやれば\N勝つだろうって…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.80,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Whadda ya think? Not bad, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ？ 別に悪くねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:03.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホ… ホントに\Nこの作戦で戦ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:03.50,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,H-Have you really been fighting with this strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.91,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）お… おうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく全滅しなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.94,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you haven't been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）えっ？\N（尾平）ほらな ほらな！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.92,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Hey, see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥）やっぱ 作戦が ひでえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.07,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,I knew our strategies friggin' sucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:15.25,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Is there no one else here who's skilled at war tactics?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:15.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）ほかに\N軍略に明るい人間は いないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.95,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,Well, ya see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:19.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥）…んなこと言われても\N俺たちは もともと農民歩兵だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.95,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,we're all original peasant soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:21.52,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,What about the Guobei Unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:25.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,郭備(かくび)隊は？ 元郭備隊の中には\N戦術の分かる人間がいるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:25.33,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,There must be someone from the former Guobei Unit that knew strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（元郭備隊兵）\Nムリだ！ 我々は完全な武闘派集団
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:29.23,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We're totally a fighter group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:32.59,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We relied on Lord Guobei for all of the strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:32.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,作戦は全部 郭備さま頼みだった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:35.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほらな！\Nつうわけで やっぱり俺らが…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:33.97,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.47,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So I guess we'll just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.84,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）やめろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 真面目にやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.91,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Hey, be serious about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:42.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）いや 真面目なんだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.60,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Uh, I am being serious, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.60,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Anyhow,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:48.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）とにかく 今 飛信隊の\N置かれている状況は非常にマズイ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:47.81,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,the state the Feixin Unit has been left in is extraordinarily bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:52.94,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Losing a lot as a reserve unit is a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:52.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,援軍という立場で\N負けまくっているのは大問題だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:58.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信の千人将降格というウワサも\Nはっきり言って現実味を帯びている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:58.24,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,And to be honest, the rumors of Xin losing his rank of Thousand-Man General are seeming more likely to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:16:59.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）えっ？\N（尾平）マ… マジか！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:16:59.99,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,F-For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:04.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）…かといって\N隊の中での対処法もないと来ている
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.97,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Having said that, there doesn't seem to be any way to deal with it within the unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:08.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,被害が少なかったのは\Nただ 強敵と出会わなかっただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:09.00,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,But the fact that you haven't had all that many losses is only because you haven't come up against any strong enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:13.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言っとくが 今の飛信隊なら―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:16.51,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,You should be aware that as it is now, the Feixin Unit could be slaughtered by 300 of the Yuehua Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:16.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽華(がくか)隊300人で皆殺しにできるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:21.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒイッ！ ヤ… ヤバイぞ マジで\N（田永(でんえい)）ど… どうすんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:20.00,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,This is seriously bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.26,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Wh-What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.57,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,With it having come to this, we have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:23.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（崇原(すうげん)）こうなったら しかたない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:26.30,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,We'll have to get Vice Captain Qiang Lei to come back to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:26.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり\N一度 羌瘣副長に戻ってもらって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:26.94,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だ… だけど…\N（信）それは絶対にダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.20,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.02,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That's one thing we definitely can't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ… しかたないな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.03,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:40.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じいちゃんの本陣では\N信に救われた部分もあったし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:40.90,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I guess there were some people in Grandpa's headquarters that were saved by you, Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで一応 恩を返しとくか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:43.04,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I suppose I can pay my debt to you back with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.29,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:46.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊に―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:50.08,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I'll call out one outstanding strategist I know to the Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の知ってる 飛び切りの軍師を\N１人 呼んでやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐ… 軍師？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:52.25,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,A-A strategist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:55.09,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Well, he's my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）まあ 俺の弟なんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:58.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ざけんな！ お前の弟なんて\N勝手に呼ぶんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.25,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.71,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't just go calling your little brother to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:01.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）いいから\N素直に俺の言うことを聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:01.30,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Please, just listen to what I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:05.31,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Once you're a Thousand-Man Unit, you cannot fight on momentum alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:05.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,千人隊は もはや\N勢いだけで戦える規模じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:09.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,作戦を組み立てる人間が\N必要不可欠なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.11,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Someone that can form battle tactics is indispensable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令Ｃ）\N報告！ 軍師どのが貝野(かいや)を通過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:19.82,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.27,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Our strategist is going to be passing through Beiye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:24.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３日後には ここに到着します！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.28,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He will arrive here in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）やっぱ 気に食わねえ\N（尾平たち）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.13,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I really don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,軍師ってからには あれこれ\N俺らに指図してくるっつう話だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.69,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Just because this guy's a strategist,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:33.11,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,he's gonna be telling us what do all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突然 現れた よそ者がよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.59,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Some outsider that just showed up out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ やっぱ気に食わねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:38.32,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It really rubs me the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:41.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！\N今は文句言える状況じゃねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:41.30,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin, this isn't the time to be complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙恬が この話をしてから10日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:44.31,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,It's been 10 days since our talk with Meng Tian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:46.80,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,And just like I thought, we haven't been able to pull off one win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺らは\Nやっぱり１勝もできなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで５連敗だぞ ５連敗！\N（信）ケッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:49.06,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,That made 5 losses in a row, for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:52.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）だからって ここまで来て\Nよそ者に頼るのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:52.58,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,So because of that, we have to rely on an outsider?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:55.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,田永…\N（去亥）恥の上塗りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:53.54,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Tian Yong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:55.24,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,It's doubly shameful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:59.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙恬の弟か何か知んねえが\N部外者によ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:59.11,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,I don't care if it is Meng Tian's little brother or whatever, he's an outsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.27,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,You guys, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:01.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… お前らまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:04.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ハアッ！\N（尾平）あっ… 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:04.73,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:10.14,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,On the flip side of being a tightly-knit unit that's fought together for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\Nそれなりに長く続いている隊では
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,内部の絆が強い反面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,部外者の介入に対し\N拒絶反応を示す場合がある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:13.79,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,sometimes there can be rejection to let in outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:20.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,百人隊から始まった飛信隊でも\Nその現象は顕著に表れた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.59,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,And even with the Feixin Unit that started from being a Hundred-Man Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.85,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,this phenomenon was pronounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:26.11,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Like hell I'm putting their lives in the hands of the\N instructions of some guy that's not even one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:26.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間でもねえヤツの指図に\Nあいつらの命 預けられっかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:31.48,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,But the Feixin Unit lost in the next battle as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:31.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）しかし\N次の戦いでも 再び飛信隊は敗れた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.56,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,Having lost an important bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:35.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,要所の橋を失い 里井の守備は―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:39.36,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,Lijing's defenses were pushed back to the inner side of a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:39.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,川の内側まで\N押し込まれる形となったのである
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:46.41,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,And then finally, the carriage carrying the strategist arrived at the Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:46.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようやく 飛信隊のもとへ\N軍師の乗った車が到着した
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:52.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どの 来ましたよ 出迎えましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.91,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:52.54,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Let's go greet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日辺りでしたっけ？\N飛信隊に蒙毅(もうき)さんが着くのは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:02.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I think it should be around today that Meng Yi arrives at the Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:06.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　いよいよ\Nあとがなくなっちゃったしね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:06.50,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yeah, finally. They're really up against a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:09.06,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Though they're not really eager about the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗り気じゃないだろうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 弟のことだから\Nうまくやるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:11.25,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,But, this is my little brother after all, so I'm sure it'll go fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.69,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Good to see you again, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙毅）お久しぶりです 兄上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:22.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ ええ～っ？\N蒙毅 なんで お前が ここに？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:22.33,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Meng Yi, what're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:25.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙毅）えっ？ なんでって…\N連絡しましたよね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:26.07,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Why? You were contacted, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:29.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここ微子城(びしじょう)で任務があるので\N軍師の件はムリだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:30.23,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,I have a task here in Weizi Castle, so I couldn't perform the strategist duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いてませんか？\N（蒙恬）き… 聞いてない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.90,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Did you not hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.68,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,N-No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.83,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Th-Then what about the Feixin Unit's strategist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… それじゃ 飛信隊の軍師は？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 代理の者を送りましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.84,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Well, I sent a representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だ… 代理の者？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.26,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,A representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:50.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（護衛兵）どうぞ 着きました
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All right, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:54.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（軍師）よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:54.98,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）何だ これー！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.74,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:14.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なんで お前が ここに？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:15.02,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:16.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）えっ？ 知り合い？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.75,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Y-You know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:20.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂(てん)）\Nハハハッ… やっぱり驚いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.67,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:26.52,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I honestly thought I wouldn't show up like this for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正直 こういう形で\Nお前の前に現れるのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:29.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと先のことだと思ってたから\N俺自身も ちょっと驚いてんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.73,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Even I was kinda surprised this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:32.43,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,But I guess it's not really the time for saying stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:32.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことも\N言ってらんない状況だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:39.04,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I'm here to help, Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:39.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）助けに来てやったぞ 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.26,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Diao!
